channel.description:
dear peaple
i am a newby and i downloaded a source of a 317 server but i wanne set a new home i a town called releca or something like that but i need to remove houses and objects can someone pls help me and say where i can find the files of the objects like a table and a chair and stuff and the map where i can find the files to remove houses.
grtz timzagers

item.title: How to remove objects and houses
item.dc:creator: @kickingjamie kickingjamie
item.description:
@kickingjamie wrote:

You can remove objects like chairs, banks, tables, barrels ect in the “deletethatobject” method - it might not be that exact name but it will be along those lines.

For map objects; the ones that you can’t right click and examine you’ll need to edit things client sided and I have no idea how.

Read full topic
